text: Grigoryevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Ashkadarsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 86 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Sterlitamak, 4 km from Novofyodorovskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Grigoryevka, Sterlitamaksky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
